{"tid":912781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慶生醉酒指罵男友　壽星女膠刀切腹送院","createTime":"2018-11-23T02:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T03:55:44.000Z","uid":6497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8940127121f0152711b644423038c6a735bcd7","tid":912781,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181123/large/1542929163_f357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181123%2Flarge%2F1542929163_f357.jpg&h=f6f4d3b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅磡黃埔花園發生自殘事件。凌晨2時許，一名34歲姓馮女子生日，其男友偕數名朋友為她慶生，其間女事主疑因醉酒，突然情緒激動力數男友不是，未幾更取出切蛋糕用的膠刀切腹，男友見狀大驚，上前奪刀，同時報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n救護員趕至現場，發現女事主清醒，腹部流血，立即為她止血再送院治理。事主其後稱是意外受傷，並無尋死之意。警方調查後相信事件沒可疑，不涉刑事成分，案件改列「糾紛」處理。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，女事主較早前與男友疑因感情問題鬧翻，惟一直藕斷絲連沒有分手。"},{"pid":"c923358f55f88088ec615d4b504a85b128ee88c8","tid":912781,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"<del>隻豬</del>條女咁撚大隻嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f9b7003b451a587cc204ab1ee3f6d0df5dd022","tid":912781,"uid":49868,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:43:51.000Z","msg":"膠刀切腹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2227e1f82a9bb57a59fb490bde88cc0df13262f5","tid":912781,"uid":9116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 膠刀切腹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4660ac38036e4bacb1a200d2b2ed840f64e622","tid":912781,"uid":46042,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018